950908.name: Marvelous Vending Machine
950908.desc:
A highly convenient Lawson vending machine with an endless supply of beverages. Sometimes, however, it dispenses something rather unusual instead.
"Just get the soft drink. Don't worry, I'll take care of the rest," says the store clerk who likes fishing.

950909.name: Eye-Catching Painting
950909.desc:
A painting of Mr. Mew looking rather dignified. When you're staring at the black cat, the black cat is also staring back at you.
"That's why I keep telling you, don't keep looking at the painting," says Mr. Mew to someone as they walk by.

950910.name: Refreshment Stop
950910.desc:
A daily stop for Aether Gazer's employees.
Every cup of coffee from this highly advanced coffee machine has a mellow flavor and does the job of dispelling sleepiness particularly well, thanks to the use of premium coffee beans from high-quality production areas and sophisticated extraction techniques.

950911.name: Comfortable Stool
950911.desc: This light and comfortable round stool provides rest to customers tired from being on the move. In the cool nights of fall, it is an absolute pleasure to sit here with a cup of piping-hot oden.

950912.name: Kitty Rug
950912.desc: A plush and soft-looking rug with Mr. Mew's face on it. Every time you step on it, you can help but hear Mr. Mew going "Welcome!" in your head.

950913.name: Round Table
950913.desc: A sturdy and practical round table around which people can sit to dine and rest. You may not know each other, but you can still chat like friends and trade interesting stories here if you like.

950914.name: Super-busy Checkout Counter
950914.desc:
The business part of the store during peak hours. The clerk rings up an endless stream of customers and bids farewell to each and every one of them with a smile.
"Thank you, please come again!"

950915.name: Food Prep Counter
950915.desc:
This clean and tidy food prep counter is always giving off the tempting aroma of food.
Delicious meals are produced here to satisfy every hungry customer.

950916.name: Teatime Snack
950916.desc:
Soft and chewy glutinous rice dumplings in three colors. A sweet snack that you can reward yourself with after a busy day.
"Have some, Admin. But be careful not to choke on them. There's plenty of them to go around," says the considerate store clerk.

950917.name: Happiness Maker
950917.desc:
An ice cream machine offering a variety of flavors. But be careful not to overfill the cone!
"Do I really have to dish up the ice cream? It's so c-c-c-cold...." says the store clerk who was made to take over this task for the time being.

950918.name: Collection Counter
950918.desc: If you're who are in a hurry, you can place an order in advance. Your order will be placed here, waiting to start a new journey with you.

950919.name: Special Beanbag (Pink)
950919.desc:
A special beanbag.
An ultra soft beanbag chair—simply flop into it and feel all your troubles melt away.

950920.name: Special Beanbag (Green)
950920.desc:
A special beanbag.
An ultra soft beanbag chair—simply flop into it and feel all your troubles melt away.

950921.name: Special Beanbag (Purple)
950921.desc:
A special beanbag.
An ultra soft beanbag chair—simply flop into it and feel all your troubles melt away.

950922.name: A Cup of Kindness
950922.desc: Ouch! Deep breaths, deep breaths! Special springtime tea for influencers, steeped in sunshine and happiness!

951001.name: Relaxing Bed
951001.desc: A bed that can restore Modifiers of any fatigue. Just lie on it and be whisked off to sleep in an instant!

951002.name: Bar Module (Corner)
951002.desc: The corner of a jointed bar counter. Would it be better after adding collision protectors onto it?

951003.name: Bar Module (Side Table)
951003.desc: The side table of a jointed bar counter. Freely use your imagination to assemble it however you like!

951004.name: Open-plan Kitchen
951004.desc: An open-plan kitchen equipped with necessary utensils. Share the joy of cooking with everyone!

951005.name: Ergonomic Chair
951005.desc: A perfectly contoured ergonomic chair. Sit as long as you like and never get tired!

951006.name: Computer Desk
951006.desc: A computer desk equipped with cutting-edge technology from the Cryptics. But do you think it seems a bit too formal?

951007.name: Holographic Projector
951007.desc: A holographic projector with advanced imaging technology. Behold the perfect quality!

951008.name: Fabric Carpet
951008.desc: A surprisingly comfortable carpet despite how plain it looks.

951009.name: Sofa Module (Left)
951009.desc: A sofa module that can be assembled according to your own preference.

951010.name: Sofa Module (Right)
951010.desc: A sofa module that can be assembled according to your own preference.

951011.name: Sofa Module (Middle)
951011.desc: A sofa module that can be assembled according to your own preference.

951012.name: Viewing Terminal
951012.desc: A glass window with added image analysis functions. If you look through the glass, you may collect unexpected data!

951013.name: Matte Wall
951013.desc: A high-tech wall with sound absorption and insulation. It's unknown what it's made from exactly, maybe some sort of composite?

951014.name: Tech Floor
951014.desc: A plain-looking high-tech floor that seems to be able to clean itself.

951017.name: Vertical Bookcase
951017.desc: A simple vertical bookcase with considerable space inside!

951018.name: Horizontal Bookcase
951018.desc: A simple horizontal bookcase. It doesn't provide much storage space but is much easier to move around!

951019.name: Lounger
951019.desc: A soft, comfortable lounger that allows for the relaxation of both the body and mind.

951020.name: Coffee Table
951020.desc: A coffee table made for tea breaks. Place some snacks on it!

951021.name: Potted Plant
951021.desc: Placed around Aether Gazer's office to purify the air.

951022.name: Swivel Stool
951022.desc: A low stool that can rotate, but it's a bit tiring when sitting for too long...

951023.name: Bar Module (Drinks)
951023.desc: A bar counter module with drinks on it. Freely use your imagination to assemble it however you like!

951024.name: Sofa Bed (Extension)
951024.desc: An extension futon for a sofa bed, allowing you to extend the sofa bed to any size you want!

951025.name: Sofa Bed (Backrest)
951025.desc: A sofa bed backrest that can be assembled when you have guests over!

951026.name: Sofa Bed (Mat)
951026.desc: One of the accessories for the sofa bed. Can be used together with the sofa bed, or independently as well!

951027.name: Normal Days
951027.desc: Room background for Normal Days. Changing the background will also change the ambient lighting effects.

951028.name: Closet
951028.desc: Open it and check for new clothes!

951101.name: Reading Time
951101.desc: A low table fully equipped with its own lighting, great for reading ancient scrolls or passing the time!

951102.name: Tea Table
951102.desc: A low table fully-prepared with tea sets and snacks. Sip on tea while chatting with friends here!

951103.name: Blackwood Chessboard
951103.desc: Solid wood chessboard made by Tian Lu Traders. Find an expert chess player and enjoy the game with them!

951104.name: Cypress Wall Lamp
951104.desc: A traditional wall lamp from Xu Heng District that gives off an imposing and rustic feel. The use of pine resin makes it more durable!

951105.name: Cypress Floor Lamp
951105.desc: A traditional floor lamp from Xu Heng District that gives off an imposing and rustic feel. The use of pine resin makes it more durable!

951106.name: Return of the Crane (Decorative Painting)
951106.desc: A decorative painting of the popular crane featured in Xu Heng District traditional folklore. Meticulously made with traditional lacquer and inlay techniques.

951107.name: Cypress Fence (Corner)
951107.desc: A traditional fence from Xu Heng District that gives off an imposing and rustic feel. The use of pine resin makes it more durable, it's said to be able to stand the test of time!

951108.name: Cypress Fence (Straight)
951108.desc: A traditional fence from Xu Heng District that gives off an imposing and rustic feel. The use of pine resin makes it more durable, it's said to be able to stand the test of time!

951109.name: Cypress Bench (Left)
951109.desc: A traditional bench from the Xu Heng District, it can be assembled according to your own needs and is able of greatly relieving fatigue.

951110.name: Cypress Bench (Middle)
951110.desc: A traditional bench from the Xu Heng District, it can be assembled according to your own needs and is able of greatly relieving fatigue.

951111.name: Cypress Bench (Right)
951111.desc: A traditional bench from the Xu Heng District, it can be assembled according to your own needs and is able of greatly relieving fatigue.

951112.name: Cypress Bench (Extension)
951112.desc: A traditional bench from the Xu Heng District, it can be assembled according to your own needs and is able of greatly relieving fatigue.

951113.name: Cypress Bench (Chaise Louge)
951113.desc: A traditional bench from the Xu Heng District, it can be assembled according to your own needs and is able of greatly relieving fatigue.

951114.name: Jade Scroll Pot
951114.desc: A jade scroll pot for storing scrolls, it's said that people often put money in it and flip it over... Perhaps it leads to an unexpected surprise?

951115.name: Agarwood Bookcase
951115.desc: A vertical bookcase that perfectly combines the craftsmanship of golden engravings with agarwood. It's said to have received high praise when placed atop a potted Huangshan pine as decoration.

951116.name: Agarwood Desk
951116.desc: A desk that perfectly combines the craftsmanship of golden engravings with agarwood. The scrolls stacked on top are no less than the amount found in a scroll pot.

951117.name: Agarwood Stool
951117.desc: A stool that perfectly combines the craftsmanship of golden engravings with agarwood. Excluding low-key luxury, sitting on it is surprisingly relaxing.

951118.name: Agarwood Window Frame
951118.desc: A window frame made primarily from agarwood, emitting a graceful, yet subtle fragrance.

951119.name: Dusk on Mountain Peaks
951119.desc: A majestic viewing platform that projects the Xu Heng District's mountains at dusk. Amidst the mist, the mountains have an ink-like texture which presents a hazy beauty.

951120.name: Subtle Fragrance
951120.desc: A red plum blossom arrangement taken from deep winter in Xu Heng District and preserved with The Cryptics' special technology. In Xu Heng, it's said to be known as the greatest of the four lords comprised of plum, orchid, bamboo, and chrysanthemum.

951121.name: Agarwood Wall Decor
951121.desc: Wall decoration made primarily from agarwood, emitting a graceful, yet subtle fragrance.

951122.name: Return of the Crane (Folding Screen)
951122.desc: A screen partition with the popular crane featured in Xu Heng District traditional folklore. Meticulously made with traditional lacquer and inlay techniques, shimmering with light when viewed up close.

951123.name: Agarwood Guqin Table
951123.desc: A table that perfectly combines the craftsmanship of golden engravings with agarwood. A perfect place for lovers of traditional music to place their guqin.

951124.name: Wandering Clouds
951124.desc: A viewing terminal that displays Xu Heng District's landscapes. It seems almost possible to hear the chiming of flutes and singing of cranes when gazing into the distance.

951125.name: Agarwood Bed
951125.desc: A Xu Heng soft bed with agarwood framing and silk bedding. Lying on it will take you off to sleep in an instant!

951126.name: Bluestone Carpet
951126.desc: A carpet with the same tones as bluestone but unusually soft texture. Simple and rustic, but very practical for daily use!

951127.name: Bluestone Wall
951127.desc: A wall made from bluestone with silk wallpaper carvings. Ancient charm with the indistinct scent of ink.

951128.name: Bluestone Floor (Fence)
951128.desc: Made primarily of bluestone and exquisitely-polished floor tiles. The surrounding fencing prevents any unexpected knocks against them.

951131.name: Memories of a Red Nightfall
951131.desc: Room background for Memories of a Red Nightfall. Changing the background will also change the ambient lighting effects.

951201.name: Nostalgic Fireplace
951201.desc: A fireplace holding many memories on its mantel. The Cryptics may not rely on traditional heating methods anymore, but for some reason, they've kept the appearance of the fireplace maintained.

951202.name: Green Forest Stool
951202.desc: Suede and oak organically come together in this round stool, which is normally used as a dining chair.

951203.name: Tea Break
951203.desc: An oak dining table laden with an inexhaustible assortment of desserts!

951204.name: Sweet Forest Dream
951204.desc: A chocolate strawberry cake on a table that never loses its freshness—How is that even possible?

951205.name: Forest Tea Party
951205.desc: A table for tea parties. The tea is always just the right temperature, so go ahead and enjoy it with a few friends!

951206.name: Oak Dinner Table
951206.desc: An oak dinner table dressed with a velvet tablecloth that seems to have a self-cleaning feature—keeping it spotless at all times!

951207.name: Triumphant Dream
951207.desc: As you drift off to sleep, you seem to be visited by dreams of the triumphs of bygone kings.

951208.name: Old King's Musings
951208.desc: Once serving as a meditation carpet, it was the king's favorite carpet.

951209.name: New King's Coronation
951209.desc: They say a king was crowned on this chair. Maybe sitting on it will give you a glimpse into that experience.

951210.name: Exotic Flower
951210.desc: A flower from a faraway land. Its splendid hue seems to wordlessly convey memories of the past...

951211.name: Exotic Potted Plant
951211.desc: A decidedly tenacious, prickly plant that grows in tropical deserts.

951212.name: Oak Fence
951212.desc: Custom oak fencing with an air of elegance.

951213.name: Oak Fence
951213.desc: Custom oak fence corner with an air of elegance. It even comes with safety padding!

951214.name: Wild Landscape
951214.desc: As you look out over the untamed wilderness, you can almost hear the wind languidly brushing over a thick forest in the distance...

951215.name: Artificial Greenery
951215.desc: A custom Yggdrasill potted plant! It may be evergreen, but is it actually a real plant?

951216.name: Cultured Collection
951216.desc: Hundreds of exotic texts fill this bookcase. Reading every last one would take some time!

951217.name: War Table
951217.desc: When it comes to conquest, generals and warriors seem to like gathering around tables like these to talk tactics.

951218.name: Yggdrasill Signet
951218.desc: Engraved with the seal of Yggdrasill, this wooden decorative painting quietly preserves this honor to this day.

951219.name: Ceremonial Stool
951219.desc: A round seat to match the Round Table of Glory. It may look vintage, but it can make a 360 turn!

951220.name: Round Table of Glory
951220.desc: It's said that those who sit around this table are equals.

951221.name: Verdant Moments
951221.desc: Room background for Verdant Moments. Changing the background will also change the ambient lighting effects.

951222.name: Yggdrasill Wallpaper
951222.desc: Yggdrasill-themed wallpaper. It looks vintage, but it's actually highly insulating!

951223.name: Yggdrasill Floor
951223.desc: Yggdrasill-themed floor tiles. It looks vintage, but it's actually slip-proof! Wanna test it out?

951301.name: Sticky Sofa
951301.desc: A sofa that looks like a sticky rice dumpling. Relevant ingredients are decorative only and not intended for consumption!

951302.name: Bamboo Leaf Dragon Boat
951302.desc: A rowing machine made to look like a dragon boat. It smells like sticky rice dumpling leaves. Burn twice the calories with half the effort!

951401.name: Summer Bench
951401.desc: A bench made from palm wood. Sitting on it with friends and chatting as you look out over the sea sounds like a lovely idea.

951402.name: Summer Break
951402.desc: A bench stocked with towels—the perfect place for a short rest after splashing around in the shallows!

951403.name: Prepare to Dive
951403.desc: A bench where people can get ready to go diving. Be careful if it's your first time!

951404.name: Sailing Memory (Left)
951404.desc: Through the widely used portholes on cruise liners, a captain cutting a heroic, daring figure was seen braving the wind and the waves!

951405.name: Sailing Memory (Center)
951405.desc: Through the widely used portholes on cruise liners, a captain cutting a heroic, daring figure was seen braving the wind and the waves!

951406.name: Sailing Memory (Right)
951406.desc: Through the widely used portholes on cruise liners, a captain cutting a heroic, daring figure was seen braving the wind and the waves!

951407.name: Angling Enthusiast
951407.desc: A rack of fishing rods available to rent. Pick a scenic platform and fish your cares away!

951408.name: Summer Carpet
951408.desc: For some reason, when your feet touch this summer special, it feels like you're walking on the beach.

951409.name: Summer Round Table
951409.desc: A round table with a cool color scheme and piled high with fruit and specialty drinks. Just looking at it is refreshing!

951410.name: Sandbank Starfish
951410.desc: A starfish left on the beach at low tide. If you touch its arms, you may get a surprising response.

951411.name: Midsummer Gate
951411.desc: Through this doorway, you'll find a relaxing vacation in the height of summer!

951412.name: Sand Pile
951412.desc: Sand piles children play with at the beach, along with scattered surfboards and beach toys.

951413.name: Clear Skies, Blue Sea
951413.desc: Clear summer skies! Sandy ocean beaches! These are our summer memories!

951414.name: Water Gun Fight
951414.desc: Remember those water gun fights at the beach? Hehe, this is a souvenir. Find somewhere nice to hang it up!

951415.name: Beach Footprints
951415.desc: Water marks left by your feet as you wade through the shallows. That's another hallmark of the beach, isn't it?

951416.name: Beach Lounger
951416.desc: A blue and white lounge chair that perfectly complements that summer beach feel.

951417.name: Summer Suitcase
951417.desc: A vintage summer suitcase. Its built-in compression technology allows it to contain far more than it looks like it should.

951418.name: Oxygen Tank
951418.desc: A special beach oxygen tank that keeps new divers safe!

951419.name: Beach Pool
951419.desc: A beachfront pool with rubber duckies and various blow-up toys floating on it. Careful not to collide with other Mods when you slide in!

951420.name: Swim Ring
951420.desc: With a swim ring, even a landlubber can—Um? Huh?! It won't come off!

951421.name: Bathing Pool
951421.desc: For water-averse Mods, this bath might be the perfect summer compromise.

951422.name: Summer Folding Char (Yellow)
951422.desc: A special summer folding chair. That yellow canvas looks pretty durable!

951423.name: Summer Folding Char (Green)
951423.desc: A special summer folding chair. That green canvas looks pretty durable!

951424.name: Beach Umbrella
951424.desc: Nothing says "beach" like a beach umbrella. Supposedly, it has a UPF of 100!

951425.name: Beach Floor
951425.desc: Beach-themed flooring. Made of fast-drying materials, it's the perfect companion for playing in the water!

951426.name: Beach Wall
951426.desc: A beach-themed wall. Its blue and yellow color scheme evokes memories of long holidays at the beach.

951427.name: Spotless Sky
951427.desc: Nothing sticks with you more than the image of a clear, endless summer sky.

951428.name: Lazy Vacation Set
951428.desc: A lounging corner complete with a parasol table and chairs. Kicking back on a recliner and gazing into the distance is never a bad idea.

951501.name: Moon Reunion
951501.desc:
A custom mooncake from the backyard kitchen. Call over some friends and dig in!
—"Wherever we are, the moon brings us together."

951502.name: Ballad of the Moon
951502.desc:
A classic sofa with a sweet osmanthus tree as the background.
—"I recall a pair of red cassias in mid-autumn. In my cup, I saw its flowers and the moon."

951503.name: Autumn Thoughts
951503.desc:
Classic hanging curtains with rabbit and osmanthus motifs.
—"A crisp chill disperses the evening clouds, and the Milky Way gleams softly like a jade plate."

951504.name: Dew of the Wind
951504.desc:
A quietly elegant screen accompanied by a potted osmanthus.
—"When will the moon appear? I raise my glass and ask the sky."

951505.name: Autumn Evening
951505.desc:
A mooncake box from the M.E.O.Ws!
—"Speak not of the phases of the moon or the weather. Rejoice in the now."

951506.name: Moon on the West River
951506.desc:
A fabric floor lamp featuring the shadowy silhouette of the Jade Rabbit.
—"People bask in the splendor of the moon over the West River, unaware of the hearts it has touched."

951507.name: Osmanthus Branch
951507.desc:
An osmanthus tree signboard showing birds taking flight at the moon's first light.
—"Birds take flight, plucking notes from strings. Crows are perched on trees. Cold dew silently douses the osmanthus flowers."

951601.name: Formulaic Deduction
951601.desc: A whiteboard covered in unfathomable formulas. With careful study... you still won't be able to make heads or tails of them!

951602.name: Window of Reverie
951602.desc: When the teacher talks, your gaze can't help but be drawn out the window.

951603.name: Study Notes
951603.desc: Whatever the teacher writes on the board will be a thoughtful distillation of what you've learned, right? Won't the test be a piece of cake if you could just memorize that?

951604.name: Classroom Podium
951604.desc: A podium complete with all sorts of teaching tools. Even in the absence of the teacher, it exudes an air of prestige not to be taken lightly.

951605.name: Classroom Desk
951605.desc: A typical classroom desk. Perhaps you'll find a treat hidden in its drawer?

951606.name: Desk Set (Vacation)
951606.desc: A typical classroom desk and chair set. Just sitting at it makes you feel a little nervous.

951607.name: Desk Set (Recess)
951607.desc: A typical classroom desk and chair set. Just sitting at it makes you feel a little nervous.

951608.name: Desk Set (Classroom)
951608.desc: A typical classroom desk and chair set. Just sitting at it makes you feel a little nervous.

951609.name: Desk Set (After School)
951609.desc: A typical classroom desk and chair set. Just sitting at it makes you feel a little nervous.

951610.name: Joint Bench
951610.desc: A bench made by putting a seat and footrest together. Looks perfect for an afternoon nap!

951611.name: Gate of Knowledge
951611.desc: A gateway to knowledge. That said, keep an eye on the window. Sometimes the homeroom teacher is watching!

951612.name: Clock of Time
951612.desc: A clock that's never wrong. Time is the perfect expression of life itself!

951613.name: Notice Board
951613.desc: A notice board with all kinds of important information on it. Bits and pieces of campus life are quietly pinned to it.

951614.name: Sound of Discipline
951614.desc: A wall-mounted stereo with decent amplification. Just remember to keep quiet during announcements!

951615.name: Classroom Seat
951615.desc: A typical classroom seat. Its use isn't limited to sitting and listening to the teacher!

951616.name: Classroom Footstool
951616.desc: A low footstool typical of classrooms. It's pretty stable.

951617.name: Classroom Wallpaper
951617.desc: Campus-themed wallpaper with a rustic, but reassuring style.

951618.name: Classroom Floor
951618.desc: Campus-themed flooring with a rustic, but reassuring style.

951701.name: Black Cat Candleholder
951701.desc:
A rustic candleholder.
The way the candlelight flickers looks almost like a black cat is scurrying through it!

951702.name: Twilight Footstool
951702.desc:
A footstool made from real leather with a color scheme reminiscent of twilight.
It feels so soft and comfy under your feet!

951703.name: Castle Fence (Straight)
951703.desc:
A fence that nicely complements the Halloween atmosphere.
They say it was taken directly from an old castle. What do you think? Sets the mood, doesn't it?

951704.name: Castle Fence (Corner)
951704.desc:
A fence that nicely complements the Halloween atmosphere.
They say it was taken directly from an old castle. What do you think? Sets the mood, doesn't it?

951705.name: Jack-o'-lantern
951705.desc:
A pumpkin lantern with a wicked grin.
You can almost hear "Trick or treat!" echoing in your ears as you look at its smile.

951706.name: Cobweb Carpet
951706.desc:
A fluffy carpet with a spiderweb pattern.
Will you get stuck if you lie down on it?

951707.name: Evil Spirit's Chair
951707.desc:
An armchair featuring genuine, hand-stitching leather.
Once you sit down, you won't want to get back up—it's like your body's been possessed by an evil spirit!

951708.name: Witchy Tea Table
951708.desc:
A tea table giving off an herbal fragrance.
If you were a witch, wouldn't you love to have a tea party around a table like this?

951801.name: Holy Night Pilgrimage
951801.desc:
A sleigh delivering gifts.
Do you think it gets to take in the warmth of the holy night's scenery as it rides through the darkness?

951802.name: Winter Watchman
951802.desc:
A meticulously-made snowman.
It keeps watch all winter with its round, black eyes.

951803.name: Snow-covered Chimney
951803.desc:
A chimney covered in a layer of snow.
The gifts get dropped in here, right?

951804.name: Winter Festival Special
951804.desc:
A Winter Festival pine tree adorned with twinkling lights.
You'll have to wait until after the Winter Festival dinner is over to take the candy and gifts hanging from the tree!

951805.name: Sweet Dreams Gift Box
951805.desc:
A Winter Festival gift box filled with gifts.
Guess what's in the box! Could it be the gift you've been hoping for all this time?

951806.name: Winter Carol
951806.desc:
A stocking with a little gift hidden inside.
A gift sent from the past, residing in the present, and hurrying into the future—hopefully this gift brings a smile to your face when you open it.

951807.name: Warm Snowy Light
951807.desc:
A floor lap that brightens the winter night.
Surely this warm lamp will light the paths of travelers on a winter's day?

951901.name: Awakening Firecrackers
951901.desc:
Firecrackers that are set off for New Year's Awakening.
"Firecrackers chase off the old year. The spring breeze caresses us as we make a toast."

951902.name: Out With the Old
951902.desc:
Leftover fragment from a used firecracker.
"The sound of the firecrackers still rings in our ears long after they're gone."

951903.name: Spring Is in the Air - Dining Chair
951903.desc:
A New Year's Awakening-themed footstool.
"The flowers and trees can sense spring before we do."

951904.name: Fireside Tea Set
951904.desc:
A small table with a tea set on it.
"What can be better than a nice cup of tea?"

951905.name: Sunrise Lamp
951905.desc:
A New Year's Awakening-themed floor lamp.
"Lights up the night like the rising sun."

951906.name: Floating Stars
951906.desc:
A New Year's Awakening-themed lantern.
"The colors fade and the lanterns float away."

951907.name: Arrival of Spring
951907.desc:
A New Year's Awakening-themed door banner.
"May the new spring bless all those who enter."

951908.name: Plum Blossom
951908.desc:
The plum blossoms are in full bloom.
"The early plum blossoms open in the trees, reflecting the sky."

951909.name: Table of Treasures
951909.desc:
A small table with a fresh plate of dumplings on it.
"Sometimes the simplest dishes are the best."

951910.name: Door of Auspiciousness
951910.desc:
A new door decorated especially for the New Year's Awakening.
"May the new spring bless all those who enter."

952016.desc:

A gown that's just as beautiful as you are.

1060.name: Nine-Tailed Guardian - Luwu
1060.desc:
<color=#9A9A9A>Modifier Intro</color>
A member of the Tian Lu Traders security team who is often away on missions in Sephirah Zones outside of Xu Heng. Honest and straightforward, and well-liked by her teammates. Outspoken and brooks zero injustice around her.

1061.name: Ethereal Enigma - Zhiming
1061.desc:
<color=#9A9A9A>Modifier Intro</color>
The Quad representative for Shuofang Isle, and Xu Heng's foremost scholar and researcher. She's also one of the creators of the Astral Engine, and is responsible for all of its maintenance and upkeep.

1095.name: Gray Ibis - Thoth
1095.desc:
<color=#9A9A9A>Modifier Intro</color>
Captain of the CORG Egregious Crimes Department's special ops team, no one can gather intelligence better than she can. Uses information warfare to avoid direct confrontation with criminals and thus minimize the harm done to civilians.
With her top-level security clearance in CORG's Intel Department, it sometimes feels like she knows everybody's secrets. And she's not afraid to use them if someone is threatening to impede the progress of a mission. In fact, there's little she won't stoop to if it means getting the mission done.

1284.name: Dimglare - Verthandi
1284.desc:
<color=#9A9A9A>Modifier Intro</color>
Verthandi learned the truth about herself and her past during the Hyperspace experiments, further cementing her desire to protect others. Now able to wield both Divine Grace and Bane Energy at the same time, she has a whole new attitude.

1197.name: Dreamshade - Oneiroi
1197.desc:
<color=#9A9A9A>Modifier Intro</color>
A Modifier with the ability to enter and invite others to enter dreams. Unable to fully control this ability, however, Hades has taken her into the Society of Muses, where Hades' two puppet maids look after her.

4600703.name: Courtyard Echoes (3 Days)
4600703.desc: The afternoon sun, tipsy wind, and intoxicating fragrance of flowers. This piece is an unforgettable and poignant commemoration of us.

4600803.name: Have A Dance With Me? (3 Days)
4600803.desc: This dance is just for you, Admin. The figure is graceful and smells faintly of orchids. It's hard to ascertain whether this is a moment of serenity, or just all a dream.

4600903.name: Time to Relax (3 Days)
4600903.desc: The chance encounter in the elevator has shown people a different side to Gengchen. Maybe tailor-made clothes are never as good as we want them to be?

4601003.name: Moment of Panic (3 Days)
4601003.desc: I'm always very organized with work, but for some reason I always make mistakes whenever you're nearby. I didn't know you panicked like that too.

4601103.name: Sleepwalker (3 Days)
4601103.desc: As night falls, Admin comes across a girl immersed in a sweet dream. In the silent twilight, the only thing that moves is time.
